#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:75
msgid "Patches"
msgstr "Parches"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:77
msgid ""
"Instead of autodetecting patches used by this game, force emulation of "
"certain patches.\n"
"\n"
"Available patches:\n"
"<b>common-this</b>: \"This Event\" in common events<b>dynrpg</b>: DynRPG "
"patch by Cherry<b>key-patch</b>: Key Patch by Ineluki<b>maniac</b>: Maniac "
"Patch by BingShan<b>pic-unlock</b>: Pictures are not blocked by "
"messages<b>rpg2k3-cmds</b>: Support all RPG Maker 2003 event commands in any "
"version of the engine\n"
"\n"
"You can provide multiple patches or use 'none' to disable all engine patches."
msgstr ""
"Forzar a emulación de certos parches en lugar de autodetectar os que usa "
"este xogo.\n"
"\n"
"Parches dispoñibles:\n"
"<b>common-this</b>: \"This Event\" en eventos comúns<b>dynrpg</b>: DynRPG "
"Patch por Cherry<b>key-patch</b>: Key Patch por Ineluki<b>maniac</b>: Maniac "
"Patch por BingShan<b>pic-unlock</b>: as mensaxes non bloquean "
"imaxes<b>rpg2k3-cmds</b>: soporte para todos los comandos de evento de RPG "
"Maker 2003 en calquera versión do motor\n"
"\n"
"Pode proporcionar varios parches ou usar 'ningún' para desactivar todos os "
"parches do motor."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:92 lutris/runners/scummvm.py:276
msgid "Language"
msgstr "Idioma"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:93
msgid "Load the game translation in the language/LANG directory."
msgstr "Cargar a tradución do xogo no directorio language/LANG."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:98 lutris/runners/zdoom.py:46
msgid "Save path"
msgstr "Roteiro de gardado"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:101
msgid ""
"Instead of storing save files in the game directory they are stored in the "
"specified path. The directory must exist."
msgstr ""
"En lugar de almacenar os arquivos de gardado no directorio do xogo, "
"almacénanse no roteiro especificado. O directorio debe existir."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:108
msgid "New game"
msgstr "Xogo novo"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:109
msgid "Skip the title scene and start a new game directly."
msgstr "Omitir a escena do título e empezar unha nova partida directamente."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:115
msgid "Load game ID"
msgstr "ID de carga de xogo"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:116
msgid ""
"Skip the title scene and load SaveXX.lsd.\n"
"Set to 0 to disable."
msgstr ""
"Omitir a escena do título e cargar SaveXX.lsd.\n"
"Poñer a 0 para desactivalo."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:125
msgid "Record input"
msgstr "Rexistrar entrada"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:126
msgid "Records all button input to the specified log file."
msgstr ""
"Rexistra todas as pulsacións dos botóns no arquivo de rexistro especificado."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:132
msgid "Replay input"
msgstr "Reproducir entrada"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:134
msgid ""
"Replays button input from the specified log file, as generated by 'Record "
"input'.\n"
"If the RNG seed and the state of the save file directory is also the same as "
"it was when the log was recorded, this should reproduce an identical run to "
"the one recorded."
msgstr ""
"Reproduce pulsacións de botóns dende o arquivo de rexistro especificado, tal "
"e como se xeraron en 'Rexistrar entrada'.\n"
"Debería reproducir unha execución idéntica á rexistrada se a semente RNG e o "
"estado do directorio de arquivos de gardado son tamén os mesmos que cando se "
"gardou o rexistro."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:143 lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:152
#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:161 lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:176
